dct_title_s: Plano de la ciudad de San Salvador
dct_description_sm: Shows roads, bridges, railroads, schools, churches, hospitals, pools, tanks, sports fields, parks, and important buildings. Includes index of health centers, educational centers, government buildings, churches, and buildings of public interest.
dct_creator_sm: Instituto Geográfico Nacional Ingeniero Pablo Arnoldo Guzmán
dct_publisher_sm: San Salvador : Instituto Geográfico Nacional "Ingeniero Pablo Arnoldo Guzmán," 1999.
San Salvador : Centro Nacional de Registros, 1999.
